Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:09.23,oped,,0,0,0,,風兒也好 鳥兒也罷 都不及我自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:16.28,oped,,0,0,0,,沒有翅膀就飛奔吧 不論什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:19.08,oped,,0,0,0,,心之所向 無所不及
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:34.76,oped,,0,0,0,,總是出乎想像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:41.35,oped,,0,0,0,,雖然無法做到完美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.15,oped,,0,0,0,,但我心底有一泓清泉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:50.07,oped,,0,0,0,,無論多麼消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:54.36,oped,,0,0,0,,都能讓透明之物充滿內心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:01:01.04,oped,,0,0,0,,這到底是 怎樣一種 奇妙的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:06.87,oped,,0,0,0,,讓我狂熱 讓我痛苦 讓我發笑 以致流下眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:12.67,oped,,0,0,0,,風兒也好 鳥兒也罷 都不及我自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:19.35,oped,,0,0,0,,沒有翅膀就飛奔吧 不論什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:21.60,oped,,0,0,0,,心之所向 無所不及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.02,oped,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:54.93,oped,,0,0,0,,那天的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:58.64,oped,,0,0,0,,我仍銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:04.40,oped,,0,0,0,,希望 色彩 戀愛和夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:08.28,oped,,0,0,0,,{\pos(647,717)}永不放棄的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:17.91,oped,,0,0,0,,我們雖已長大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:29.55,oped,,0,0,0,,那寶物卻永恆不變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.55,oped,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644.8,717)}沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:39.73,oped,,0,0,0,,信念就是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:46.23,oped,,0,0,0,,就算現在略有羞澀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:50.86,oped,,0,0,0,,卻也心照不宣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.03,0:23:51.95,oped,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:57.70,oped,,0,0,0,,在我們心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:01.96,oped,,0,0,0,,有一顆閃閃發光的 jewelry
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:05.59,oped,,0,0,0,,隨時隨地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:09.59,oped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,521)}都在賦予我勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:11.63,oped,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了 無精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}睡覺的時候肚子著涼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}三個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}去開晨會了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他最近好忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}身體沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那你就別讓他擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他說你全身濕透地回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 我立刻就去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}然而睡覺的時候還是涼了肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}多吃點那個 長高點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你以前說過吧 要長到電線杆那麼高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}來 這個也給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你只是不喜歡西藍花而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:59.74,biaoti,,0,0,0,,小櫻和厲害的轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻的哥哥好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他就知道欺負我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}煎餅味道如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個確實是很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}同學們早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家都回座位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天給大家介紹一位新同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}詩之本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}自我介紹一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我叫詩之本秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她的名字是這樣寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家要多跟她說說友枝中學的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有 下週開始 詩之本同學也開始值日和打掃衛生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊 很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}希望能和她成為好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抱歉 我們來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你就是大家都在議論的二班的轉學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她這麼有名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們班的人也跑去看她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我邀請她一起吃午飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你以前在香港的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 來日本之前 我住在香港
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}香港之前是法國 再之前是德國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你說還去過義大利和英國吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以我有點擔心日語說不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 不用敬語也沒關係的 反正我們一樣大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我努力學過了 可還是說得不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說到敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}基本是對上級和年長的人使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是在日本的某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}年長的人要對年齡小的人說敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}據說他們很注重禮節
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要是用錯了敬語 會被罵得很慘的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可怕吧 可怕吧 太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}山崎同學 你最近的瞎扯淡怎麼這麼沒水準
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}受害者增多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我要去找老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要去老師辦公室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你知道在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我帶你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可是 午休還沒結束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我幫你拿東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們走好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我帶你去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}感覺她們關係很融洽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然只聊了一小會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但秋穗人還挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還很率直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那你還騙人家 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼嘛 你笑都笑得這麼不走心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還讓別人幫我拿便當盒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知世和千春會幫你帶回教室的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家都好溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊 大家真的都很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻同學 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你也很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}話說回來 我們倆挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我叫木之本櫻 你叫詩之本秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}總感覺很像 特別是姓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻同學 我想和你成為好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請多多關照 小櫻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好了 下午的課開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}語文課 我好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有什麼不懂的儘管問我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然我自己也有很多不懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和上次課一樣 今天也來學習四字熟語
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請把空出來的部分填上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}遠見同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}木之本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}到上面來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我會為你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我 我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家都答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那我們來看下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一下子就寫對了四字熟語 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒什麼 我預習過了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那是錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你怎麼了 木之本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那 那個 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}外面又發生怪事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}木之本同學好像身體不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個 沒事… 不 有事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我可以帶她去醫務室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大道寺同學是保健委員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.42,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}兩個人沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗 對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一個人都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}明明還在上課 連你也陪我出來了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請別在意 畢竟有緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 你突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}院子裡的樹動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一開始只有一棵突然動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}然後就很多棵一起動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這果然又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}應該是新的卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我終於可以說那句話了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我早就料到會有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以為了以防萬一 帶上了服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我早就料到會有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以為了以防萬一 帶上了攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我就說你幹嘛要把包帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 來轉一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}簡直完美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}再多擺點造型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}拿著裙擺 歪一點頭 笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要跑到學校外面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}隱藏著夢之力量的鑰匙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在我面前顯示你真正的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知世你待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「水源」…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要是給樹澆水的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}感覺它們會更精神 然後跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「包圍」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣就跑不出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}讓結界變軟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣下去會破掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}難道說… 如果是那張卡牌的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 要是弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}覆滿大地 給予它們最後一擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「水源」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為我開闢道路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}無主之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以夢之杖 為吾之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}固著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}果然是卡牌搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好不容易說出了那句話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}明明服裝和攝影機都準備完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就是現在 為我開闢道路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是卻沒準備好拍攝被魔法包圍的小櫻的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真是嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}收服卡牌的時候 還有把樹移回去的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}都很擔心會不會有人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}它們沒有自己回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是我又一次用這張卡牌讓它們移動回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是知世拍到了之前沒拍到的使用魔法的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:50.07,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}走太快的話樹根走路的聲音會很大 所以慢慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}該死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要是跟著你去學校 我的英姿也會被拍下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以 那張卡牌到底能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「行動」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好像是能移動物體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼時候才能用到這張牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可以幫忙端茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雞肋 這也太雞肋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}它連樹都可以移動哦 才不雞肋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}果然還是感覺不到魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}用鑰匙的話就能使用它的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}關鍵也許就在那個魔杖上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 那個魔杖也是鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以直接說「關鍵就在那個鑰匙上」不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣努努力的話就變成一個冷笑話了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}關鍵和鑰匙 關鍵就是鑰匙 鑰匙也是關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我變回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們談完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}招呼都不打一聲就變身 月也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}如果月也和雪兔一樣坦率就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 要是變坦率了 那就不是月了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真想見一見另一個我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雪兔哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}茶都涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我去重新泡一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我這還有點心哦 還有水饅頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}豆餡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}豆餡 豆餡 豆餡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}豆餡 豆餡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你和桃矢說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一大早就把西藍花扔給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說叫我變成怪獸什麼的 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}果然你們倆關係很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}才不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小兔子 你感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是小櫻在背後說我壞話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}決定了 明天的早飯吃蒟蒻套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}接吧 不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我先去廚房了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我是小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你現在方便說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我現在在雪兔哥家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}月有什麼見解嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他說還是感覺不到魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也沒有發現其他在意的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}艾利歐也沒給我回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然都是些搞不懂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但我會盡力做好我力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}首先就是眼前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼你才厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還一個人住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下次 我能給你做便當嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我練習過了 不會把雞蛋煎焦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然還是沒有哥哥做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝 我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}如果發生什麼奇怪的事情就聯繫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}深夜也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就算沒有奇怪的事情 也能給你打電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}隨時都行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝你 小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}月和可魯貝洛斯都沒有發現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要說有什麼奇怪的事 也就是來了個轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是個女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 也沒感覺到有魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}占卜也是這麼顯示的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}其他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和小櫻會很投機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}感覺她們能成為好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有其他什麼奇怪的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}又得到了一張新的卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我知道你很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但現在還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我就是為了那個時刻而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:13.01,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}交給小可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.34,0:24:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家久等了 這裡是「交給小可」的環節
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.93,0:24:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這次介紹的是友枝中學的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.31,0:24:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個人是班導師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}留著短髮很可愛的守田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.48,0:24:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}感覺很溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.65,0:24:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}教授科目是語文
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.98,0:24:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是副班導師 森老師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.40,0:24:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還擔任了拉拉隊的顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.19,0:24:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}之後是小櫻不擅長的數學的老師和理科的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.24,0:24:32.24,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這次介紹的人太次要了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.95,0:24:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}透明牌的漢字讀音也越來越難了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.70,0:24:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對成為國中生的小櫻來說是個學習的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.62,0:24:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.75,0:24:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}受秋穗的邀請 大家決定一起去賞櫻花
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.79,0:24:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}便當裡的玉子燒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.29,0:24:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不知道能不能做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.50,0:24:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下集 小櫻和賞花爭奪戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.76,0:24:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和小櫻一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.13,0:24:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.51,0:24:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,
